        "content_6A636Y": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "The short version",
            "content": "<ul><li>We collect what we need to run a clean DTC business — orders, accounts, marketing preferences, and the basic web data that comes with running a site.</li><li>We don’t sell your personal information.</li><li>We share data with vendors that help us operate (payments, fulfillment, email, subscriptions, analytics). They’re held to confidentiality terms.</li><li>You can ask to see, correct, or delete your data at any time.</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "content_6PiArP": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "1. Who this policy covers",
            "content": "<p>This Privacy Policy covers personal information we collect from visitors and customers of tonique.com, our connected social and email channels, and anyone who interacts with us by email or text.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_awxwaU": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. What we collect",
            "content": "<p><strong>Information you give us directly</strong></p><ul><li><strong>Account and order details</strong> — name, email, shipping address, billing address, phone number (if you provide one), and password.</li><li><strong>Payment information</strong> — card or payment data, processed by our payment providers (Shopify Payments, Shop Pay, and similar). We don’t store full card numbers on our servers.</li><li><strong>Subscription preferences</strong> — cadence, address, payment method on file, and your skip/pause history.</li><li><strong>Marketing preferences</strong> — whether you’ve opted in to email or SMS, and what you’ve clicked.</li><li><strong>Customer service</strong> — whatever you share with us when you write in. We keep these to learn from and to follow up.</li><li><strong>Reviews and referrals</strong> — review content, referral codes you share or use.</li></ul><p><strong>Information we collect automatically</strong></p><p>Like most sites, ours uses cookies and similar tools to remember your cart, keep you logged in, measure traffic, and improve the experience. This includes:</p><ul><li>IP address, device type, browser, and operating system</li><li>Pages viewed, products clicked, time on site</li><li>Referrer URL (the link or ad that brought you here)</li><li>Cookie identifiers from analytics and advertising tools</li></ul><p><strong>Information from third parties</strong></p><p>If you sign in or interact through a third-party service (for example, Shop Pay, Apple Pay, Google, or social platforms), we may receive limited information from them — usually your name, email, and a payment token.</p>"
          }
        },
        "content_iyM4pq": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3. How we use your information",
            "content": "<p>We use your information to:</p><ul><li>Take and fulfill orders, process payments, and run subscriptions</li><li>Send you order confirmations, shipping updates, and account messages</li><li>Send marketing emails and texts you’ve opted in to</li><li>Run our referral and affiliate programs</li><li>Improve the Site, the product, and the customer experience</li><li>Run advertising and measure how it performs</li><li>Prevent fraud and keep the Site secure</li><li>Meet legal and tax requirements</li></ul>"
          }
        },
        "content_tDP4hn": {
          "type": "content",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "4. The vendors we use",
            "content": "<p>We work with a small set of trusted vendors to run Tonique. They process data on our behalf and are held to confidentiality terms. As of the launch, this includes:</p><ul><li><strong>Shopify</strong> — site hosting, checkout, and order management</li><li><strong>Recharge (or our subscription platform of record)</strong> — subscription billing and management</li><li><strong>Klaviyo</strong> — email and SMS marketing</li><li><strong>Shopify Payments / Shop Pay / Apple Pay / Google Pay</strong> — payment processing</li><li><strong>Our fulfillment and shipping partners</strong> — to pack and deliver your order</li><li><strong>Google Analytics, Meta Pixel, TikTok Pixel</strong> — site analytics and ad measurement</li><li><strong>Our reviews app</strong> — collecting and displaying reviews</li><li><strong>Our referral and affiliate platform</strong> — tracking referrals and affiliate links</li></ul><p><em>*Drafting note: This vendor list should be reconfirmed at launch and updated whenever a new tool is added or removed. Some jurisdictions require this list to be specific.</em></p>"
          }
